# UITableViewDropProposal.Intent.insertAtDestinationIndexPath

**Case**

Insert the dropped content at the specified index path.

## Declaration

```swift
case insertAtDestinationIndexPath
```

## Constants

- **UITableViewDropProposal.Intent.unspecified**: No drop proposal was specified.
- **UITableViewDropProposal.Intent.insertIntoDestinationIndexPath**: Incorporate the dropped content into the row at the specified index path.
- **UITableViewDropProposal.Intent.automatic**: Incorporate the content in an appropriate way based on the drop location.
